                    <msContents>
                        <!-- describe the intellectual content of an inscription -->
                        <summary>This plate records an endowment made by Cuppiramaṇiya Tirumalai Cētupati Rakunāta to Ampalattāṭum paṇṭāram for performing pūja in Avudaiyarkoil to honor his ancestors and Tirumalai Nāyakkar.</summary>
                        <!-- offers the possibility to give a summary of the inscription's content -->
                    </msContents>
